@startuml cicd_pipeline_flow
' CI/CD Pipeline Flow

start
:Commit / Pull Request;
:Trigger Azure Pipeline;
fork
  :Restore & Build Backend;
  :Run Backend Tests;
fork again
  :Restore & Build Frontend;
  :Run Frontend Unit Tests;
end fork

:Option: Playwright E2E Tests;

:Package Backend (DLL / Docker);
:ng build prod;
:Build Docker Images;
:Push Artifact / Container Image;
if (Deploy approved?) then (yes)
  :Deploy Stage;
  :Smoke Tests / Health Checks;
else (no)
  :Warten auf Freigabe;
endif
stop
@enduml